			<node ID="ID_1489238483" TEXT="Time Value of Money is a concept that recognizes the relevant worth of future cash flows arising as a result of financial decisions by considering the opportunity cost of funds. Time Value of Money concept facilitates an objective evaluation of cash flows arising from different time periods by converting them into present value or future value equivalents." />
